- cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper deals with privacy regulations and their impact on software architectures.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category as the paper discusses the regulatory requirements for data protection and privacy.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper may touch upon the use of machine learning in GDPR compliance.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also less likely but possible as the paper may discuss the programming languages and tools used in implementing GDPR-compliant software architectures.
